  <steps>
    <step order="1">Author `modes/draftMode.ts`:
      - `deriveDraftState(sourceRecord: IComposerSourceRecord): Partial&lt;EmailComposerState&gt;` ‚Äî populates state from existing record + marks `existingCommunicationId` for downstream use
      - `mapStateToDraftUpdate(state): Record&lt;string, unknown&gt;` ‚Äî converts state slots ‚Üí Dataverse field shape for Xrm.WebApi.updateRecord
      - `mapStateToSendRequest(state): SendCommunicationRequest &amp; { existingCommunicationId }` ‚Äî converts state ‚Üí send request including existing ID</step>
    <step order="2">Update reducer:
      - `initialState` handles `mode === 'draft' &amp;&amp; sourceRecord` ‚Äî applies `deriveDraftState`
      - New state slot: `existingCommunicationId?: string` (set when draft loads)</step>
    <step order="3">Update `EmailComposer.tsx`:
      - `saveDraft()` real impl: if `existingCommunicationId` present, call `Xrm.WebApi.updateRecord('sprk_communication', existingCommunicationId, mapStateToDraftUpdate(state))`; else fallback (compose mode draft: first-save creates a new record, sets `existingCommunicationId`)
      - `send()` for draft mode: include `existingCommunicationId` in the request body
      - `discard()` new method on imperative handle: `Xrm.WebApi.deleteRecord('sprk_communication', existingCommunicationId)` + invoke `onClose`</step>
    <step order="4">Check `communicationApi.ts` (post Wave 0 task 005) for `existingCommunicationId` field:
      - If present: use
      - If missing: add as optional field on `SendCommunicationRequest` type; coordinate with BFF ‚Äî if BFF DTO `SendCommunicationRequest.cs` doesn't have it, document gap + add an ad-hoc Wave 0 follow-up note (may require parallel BFF PR)</step>
    <step order="5">Wire ComposerActionBar's Discard button (added in task 019 for draft mode) to invoke `discard()`.</step>
    <step order="6">Smoke test in dev: load a known draft record, edit subject, click Save Draft ‚Üí record updated; reload ‚Üí edits preserved; click Send ‚Üí statuscode ‚Üí Sent + Graph SendMail invoked.</step>
    <step order="7">Run `npm run build` + `npm run lint` clean.</step>
    <step order="7.5">Step 9.5 quality gates ‚Äî code-review + adr-check.</step>
    <step order="8">Update `TASK-INDEX.md`: 027 ‚úÖ.</step>
    <step order="9">Update `current-task.md` per task-execute protocol.</step>
  </steps>

